IWC is a modern whatsapp client with a sidebar including many features

--Features--
#AI Integration (ChatGPT and Gemini and Claude)
#Auto Reply Bot
#Quick Replies
#Font Changer (changes the font you type not the apps!)
#Emoji Picker
#Privacy mode which blurs all messages and only shows when hovered
#DeepL Translation
#ChatGPT Integration
#Gemini Integration
#Claude Integration
#Screenshot Tool
#Modern Sidebar with keyboard shortcuts to use all features
#Multi account support
#Custom Themes
#GIF Searcher
